Idea
A market that can be used to look at advertisements published by active persons and make friends using it, then we can make it social market.

After we finish this website and the mobile version of the site we will have the following features:
-	Every person can have a free account. So, everyone will have his/her profile after he/she completes the sign up steps.
-	Users can add products, buy and rate other products, make a comment on a product, add another person as friend then chat with each other (just like any other social website like the facebook).
-	We will make a mobile program for the website, it contains the same and extra features like the notification for things that happen at someone’s social network e.g: new friend request, new product, etc…
-	We  will be able to connect with social networks like facebook and twitter. Then we can sign up for the website by the social network account, and we may share product on other social media sites (facebook and twitter).

